Malice/ Hellplague:
 
Malice opened a channel to Rodimus, speaking softly.
 
"Rodimus, we are returning to base with Hellplague and her companion."
 
Hellplague walks with Celeron, wishing they could fly and get there quicker.

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
Celeron remained silent, but nodded in agreement.  He didn't fully
trust them, but was eager to get away from this place.

He didn't really care about his weapons because he had just assembled
them from the junk in the storage room and they were not especially
useful to him.


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
